lead_paragraph: The names of hotels and other facilities in Yosemite National Park will change in a battle over who owns the intellectual property.
snippet: The names of hotels and other facilities in Yosemite National Park will change in a battle over who owns the intellectual property.

headline.main: California: Yosemite Will Change Hotel Names
headline.print_headline: California: Yosemite Will Change Hotel Names

abstract: Spokesman for Yosemite National Park says names of hotels and other facilities in the park will change due to dispute with New York company Delaware North, which lost bid to run park's facilities and says that it paid for intellectual property behind concessions in question.
